@@TJvTipOfDayOption
<TITLE TJvTipOfDayOption type>
Summary
  Defines values that determine the behavior of a Tip of the Day dialog.
Description
  The TJvTipOfDayOption type defines values that determine the appearance and behavior of a Tip of
  the Day dialog.

  \TJvTipOfDayOption is a set of TJvTipOfDayOptions values.
@@TJvTipOfDayOption.toShowOnStartUp
  Specifies whether the checkbox on the dialog is checked or unchecked. Also, if no
  <LINK TJvTipOfDay.OnCanShow,OnCanShow> event handler is used, it determines whether the dialog is 
  shown on start up of the application. 
                    
  Use flag toShowOnStartUp before calling Execute, to
  specify whether the checkbox must be checked or unchecked. Use flag toShowOnStartUp
  after calling <LINK TJvTipOfDay.Execute,Execute>, to determine whether the checkbox was checked or
  unchecked when the user closed the dialog.
@@TJvTipOfDayOption.toUseRegistry
  Specifies whether to use the built-in method - that uses the registry - to store the 
  value of the checkbox. 
@@TJvTipOfDayOption.toShowWhenFormShown
  Shows the tip dialog when the parent form of the TJvTipOfDay component is shown.
